metadata.name: Los aljibes manantiales
metadata.description: Digital Collage. 3023x4249px. It comes from a gouache and ink drawing. It has, among other things, parts of my oil paintings and digital drawings made in a Spectrum ZX program. The title of the work is taken from a verse of the song "Conmigo" by Hugo Fatorusso, which today came back to my head after a long time. Montevideo, March 2023
